data.title: Massachusetts Executive Office of Health And Human Services
data.text:
How to search for a Public Health Radiologic Technologist

You can search for a Public Health Radiologic Technologist by last name or number. Remember that there could be more than one radiologic technologist with the same last name.

Please be sure to note the expiration date of the technologist's license. Although an individual has been licensed in the Commonwealth, the individual may no longer have a valid license in accordance with the expiration date shown.
